
'''Apafram Afahyɔ''' yɛ afehyia afahyɛ a ahenfo ne wɔn manfoɔ a wɔn wɔ Akwamu a ɛwɔ Apuei Mantam no di wo Ghana<ref>https://tourghana.com/ghana-festivals/</ref><ref>https://www.ghanaconsulatedubai.com/tourism.html</ref><ref>https://tourghana.com/ghana-festivals/</ref>. Wodi saa afahye yi wɔ ɔpepɔn bosome no mu<ref>https://www.slutchtours.com/?page_id=21</ref><ref>https://touringghana.com/festivals/</ref><ref>https://www.amazon.com/Akwamu-Odwira-Apafram-festival/dp/B0006DYDCM</ref><ref>https://www.ghanaconsulatedubai.com/tourism.html</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Ahenfo no bɔ dwa dataa wɔ afahyɛ no bere mu. Wɔsoa wɔn akannifo no wɔ wɔn apakan ahorɔw mu. Wɔde nnwomtoɔ ne asa nso ka ho<ref>Apafram Festival</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
Wodi afahyɛ yi de hyɛ twaka a eda wɔn ne wɔn nananom nsamanfoɔ ntam no den na afei, wɔde srɛ ahobammɔ afiri wɔn nkyɛn<ref>https://touringghana.com/festivals/</ref>.

